{
  "stem": "26699.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if somebody tries to hold his arms up for half an hour, will realize how difficult it is.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What about a child of six?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From time to time, the German soldier, if you can call him a soldier, was shouting at me to keep my hands up.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother-- I didn't understand what he was saying-- my mother was telling me, hold your hands up, [PAUSES] because otherwise he will shoot you.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN] This was my first lesson of a foreign language, learned and the hard way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I saw many years later the photograph of a child with hands up in Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The only difference is that I didn't have the honor of a German artist to take my picture.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES] But was no difference.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in this way, we were driven to the assembly place, which was the main police station of Iasi.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As we were coming closer, more and more people were herded into the same place, the same direction from various streets, generally by German troops who were practicing on us for what was going to happen a couple days later in Russia.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were aligned in a long, winding queue.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was like a long snake, like a serpentine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we heard shootings in the courtyard of the police station.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a wall.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People were taken by the tens, put against the wall, and machine gunned.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the queue was progressing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The line was shortening, but it was a long, long line.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were Romanian Christian [PAUSES] [CLEARS THROAT] Iron Guards taking the dead bodies and piling them up in huge piles.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I saw people there who weren't properly killed, and they were thrown like this, still alive.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
